      <title>中国持续的房地产危机导致铁矿石跌破 100 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/iron-ore-drops-below-100-on-china-s-persistent-property-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者押注中国长达数年的房地产危机将持续到 2024 年，从而抑制钢铁需求，铁矿石期货七个月来首次跌破每吨 100 美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/iron-ore-drops-below-100-on-china-s-persistent-property-crisis</guid>
