      <title>供应威胁加剧，铜价飙升至 9,000 美元以上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/copper-resumes-rally-toward-9-000-as-china-supply-tightens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铜价升至每吨 9,000 美元以上—— 11个月以来的最高水平——随着投资者对全球供应挑战将使市场重新陷入赤字的风险做出反应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/copper-resumes-rally-toward-9-000-as-china-supply-tightens</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 03:27:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>IEA 将预测转向赤字，油价维持近四个月高点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-15</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际能源署预测到 2024 年将出现供应短缺，改变了之前的盈余预测，而 OPEC+ 维持减产的前提下，油价维持在四个月高位附近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-15</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 23:28:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本井喷的工资结果可能引发日本央行三月加息的讨论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/market-players-await-wage-result-key-to-boj-rate-hike-calculus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本最大的工会组织周五宣布了强于预期的年度工资协议，这一结果将加剧人们本已强烈的猜测，即日本央行将于下周自 2007 年以来首次加息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/market-players-await-wage-result-key-to-boj-rate-hike-calculus</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 23:15:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
